com.versant.common.dataservice
Class VDSObjectManager

java.lang.Object
  com.versant.common.dataservice.VDSObjectManager

public class VDSObjectManager
extends java.lang.Object

This class manages the cache of VDSObject and VDSClass objects. It matches the signature of the packed(externalized) objects message to the registered object factories. The object factory that has the matching signature would be used to generate VDSObject and VDSClass objects.

See Also:
VDSObject, VDSClass,
